OpenSim::AbstractSpeed

AbstractSpeed Class Reference

#include <AbstractSpeed.h>

Inheritance diagram for AbstractSpeed:

Detailed Description

An abstract class that specifies the interface for a generalied speed.

Speeds usually have a one-to-one correspondence with coordinates, but they don't have to.

Author:
Peter Loan
Version:
1.0
